A random sentence generator, to show an example of using "response markup" to create dynamic text.

It generates sentences like:

the lovely mountain says "Mary likes Larry" to the peaceful tree.
Billy gives the tree to Jane.
the brown dog likes Jack.
the lawn likes the weird garden.
Jill says "Billy speaks wistfully" to Joey.
Jill writes "the benevolent mouse gives the evil garden to Jessica" on the lovely lawn.
the weird street whispers to the green flower.
the lively chair likes Carla.
Chris gives the gross cat to the peppy mouse.

